query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(q1 t1 tq1 a1) NoMergeJoin(a1 acc q1 t1 tq1 u1 b) NoMergeJoin(a1 acc b q1 t1 tq1 u1 s) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('apache',
'datagrid',
'editor',
'facebook-javascript-sdk',
'google-oauth',
'initialization',
'processing',
'r-markdown',
'react-navigation',
'teradata',
'uiview',
'winrt-xaml')
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Benefactor',
'Organizer',
'Tenacious')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
